Paper: hep-th/0001031

Date: 2000-01-07

Title: Star-Product and Massless Free Field Dynamics in $AdS_4$

Authors: K.I.Bolotin and M.A.Vasiliev (Lebedev Physical Institute)

Comments: LaTex, 12 pages, no figures; minor correction, the version to appear

in Physics Letters BJournal-ref: Phys.Lett. B479 (2000) 421-428

Generic solution of free equations for massless fields of an arbitrary spinin $AdS_4$ is built in terms of the star-product algebra with spinor generatingelements. A class of "plane wave" solutions is described explicitly.